{"tid":2366618,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"疑駕駛期間視像會議　郭偉強：已盡快在適當位置停車","createTime":"2021-01-14T15:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T02:43:49.000Z","uid":378936,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"007d773c67bdf2b40a9c8e0b51db69830c652b2c","tid":2366618,"uid":378936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:46:51.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】立法會房屋事務委員會舉行視像會議期間，工聯會郭偉強懷疑一邊駕駛一邊開會。他其後回應說，已盡快在適當位置停車。<br />\n<br />\n郭偉強應主席張宇人要求開鏡頭，見到他將立法會設定為虛擬背景，隱約見到旁邊有安全帶，似乎在車內，又不時向後望。郭偉強其後在社交平台指，已盡快在適當位置停車，繼續會議，又稱天氣寒冷，車上暖氣是他的避寒中心。<span class=\"red\">根據道路交通條例38條，任何人在道路上駕駛車輛時，如無適當的謹慎及專注，即屬不小心駕駛，最高可被判監六個月。</span><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/44227\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F44227&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVY%2FVxAEwmAwDimrVtn2syv4%3D&h=d59f97cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F44227&h=8af25a68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/44227</a>"},{"pid":"c7e166bceab3dd9fd33f72ad41e8282dd022c9b7","tid":2366618,"uid":119343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:48:37.000Z","msg":"放心，唔會告"},{"pid":"81ad3cb87f3a6d971550f5eec390db3d42f60d35","tid":2366618,"uid":378936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:51:05.000Z","msg":"推到佢仆街"},{"pid":"f413d85dc5cb540a9c9896aa57df746e1f95ac13","tid":2366618,"uid":47384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:53:50.000Z","msg":"佢好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打人都唔告啦 <br />\n呢d小意思"},{"pid":"99a497475bc318e19d3ae054fd43b135eaf2f687","tid":2366618,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f413d85dc5cb540a9c9896aa57df746e1f95ac13","tid":2366618,"uid":47384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:53